# Copy to ".env" (gitignored). Server-side only — never shipped to the browser.
#
# YOUTUBE_API_KEY powers BOTH:
#   1. The serverless endpoint /api/videos (set this as an env var in your host,
#      e.g. Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables). The site
#      fetches that endpoint at runtime, so new uploads appear with no rebuild.
#   2. The optional build-time snapshot refresh: `npm run sync:shorts`.
#
# The key is read on the server only; it is never exposed to visitors.
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=
